                        Āticempoṉṉampalatta lammāneḻun=taruḷu
                        <lb n="19" break="no"/>m vitiyum poṉmeynteṉṉāy melviḷakkum cotik koṭiyuṭaittā <surplus>poṉ</surplus> poṉṉāl kuṟukavalāṉ Oṉṟumpaṭi yamaittāṉ toṇṭaiyarko<surplus>ā</surplus>ṉ pārttu <g type="pc">.</g>
                        
