                        <lb n="21"/>mā mattak kuṉṟu kuṭutta<unclear>ruḷi</unclear> maṇṇiṟ ko<unclear>ṭuṅ</unclear>kali vārāme taṭuttāṉ toṇṭaiyar koṉ ṟāṉ <g type="pc">.</g>
                        
